segmentosSRT.text: and we have understood that message.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_11

segmentosSRT.text: It's not that we have a screw loose.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_11

segmentosSRT.text:
It’s not that we’re crazy,
or that we’re less than you.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_11

segmentosSRT.text:
It’s just that we accepted
to walk with Jesus Christ.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_11

segmentosSRT.text: That’s the difference between you and us.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_11

segmentosSRT.text: we’re here in front of the presence of God

segmentosSRT.text: and maybe you, my friend, will say:
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_11

segmentosSRT.text: Those people who come here just to sing...
